<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Usually if they publicly have a Goodreads Author account-it would say it next to her name. Though that doesn&apos;t mean she doesn&apos;t browse her reviews on <a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Usually if they publicly have a Goodreads Author account-it would say it next to her name. Though that doesn't mean she doesn't browse her reviews on her, Amazon, etc.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
